Installation
------------

If you don't have installed Java yet, install it from official Derbian repository.
Install jzmq-bundle on your system. After installation you have full support 
for ZeroMQ with Java.
Unpack hsn2-main archive. 

Launching
---------

Run hsn2-framework.jar using java -jar command with -Djava.library.path option
to set zmq library location.
For example:

java -Djava.library.path=/usr/local/lib -jar hsn2-framework.jar